# Lock files that shouldn't be edited manually
# (uv.lock and bun.lock SHOULD be committed)
# This is a Bun project: ignore stray lockfiles from other package managers so a
# wrong `npm`/`pnpm`/`yarn` run can't reintroduce them (see commit 3162e528).
pnpm-lock.yaml
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

.vercel
